  "short_description": "The latest title in the \"TGM\" series, \"TETRIS® THE GRAND MASTER 4 -ABSOLUTE EYE-\" offers the ultimate Tetris game that no one has ever experienced before. Challenge yourself in new modes such as ASUKA and SHIRANUI.",
